<P>
Good Housekeeping's new ads are a refreshing change. Those of us who have made 
an educated decision to devote our minds and skills to the nurturing of our 
families tire of being told by the media that homemakers are robbed of identity 
and are not free or self-actualized. 
</P>
<P>
MARILYN PASSWATER 
</P>
<P>
Redlands 
</P>
