<HEADLINE>
<P>
'TRADITION' AND THE WORKING WOMAN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Equal to the subtle-yet-unmistakable slam against women in the Good 
Housekeeping ad is the slam against the international community. Not only is 
the center of the world one's own home, but those English-speaking and 
(probably) all-white Girl Scouts are more important than the UNICEF cards (and, 
