Thank you for your continued efforts to put readers in touch with the many 
small inns and lodges in Southern California. You recently published a letter, 
"Small and Beautiful" (Nov. 13), from David Greenfield, one of our satisfied 
guests who was pleased with his accommodations at the San Lorenzo, 777 San 
Lorenzo Road, Palm Springs 92264, (619) 325-5166. Since that letter, we have 
been inundated with requests for our brochure and have received many confirmed 
reservations. 
</P>
