ON THE RIGHT TRACK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
My husband and I and several friends traveled to New Orleans with Rodney Pick 
of Sentimental Rail Journeys. The vintage rail cars are wonderful and 
Sentimental Rail Journeys does a great job of taking care of everybody. Food 
aboard the train also is excellent and accommodations and tours are the best! 
We highly recommend Sentimental Rail Journeys, P.O. Box 4574, Thousand Oaks 
91360, (805) 499-9306. 
