</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
TRAVEL NEWS AND BRIEFS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By NORMAN DASH 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
