<TYPE>
<P>
Brief 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
CHURCHES; CATHOLIC CHURCH -- MICHIGAN; CATHOLICS; DETROIT (MI) 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
